Odaily Planet Daily News According to Onchain Lens monitoring, two newly created wallets hoarded ETH worth $388 million, including: 
Wallet 0x3dF received 87,275 ETH from Galaxy OTC transactions, worth $326 million; 
Wallet 0x286 received 16,472 ETH from FalconX, worth $61.43 million.
